name: Customizable Pattern Kit
description:
About

Negative Space is a library of 19 component-based patterns and 22 graphic elements.


Use them for landing pages, slide decks, packaging, or anywhere else you have empty space you'd like to spruce up.


Each pattern is fully customizable, so you can experiment with different ways to change them and make them your own!


Includes:

  • 19 fully customizable patterns
  • 22 additional graphic elements
  • Full component library
  • Additional rasterized patterns for quick usage
